<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
1. Revoke the individual's certification for a minimum of 1 year. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
2. Suspend the individual's certification for 30 to 180 days. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
3. Formally reprimand the individual. 
