<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(ii) Another location that is not currently included in the institution's participation in the program, if_
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(A) That location offers 100 percent of an educational program; or
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
