<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(B) Has changed its name, location, or address.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(2) The Secretary considers the submission of the required notification under 34 CFR 600.30 with respect to that location
