<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
request and in a timely manner, information relating to the 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
administrative capability and financial responsibility of the 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
institution to_
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
