<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(ii) The State postsecondary review entity designated under 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
subpart 1 of part H of Title IV of the HEA for the State or 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
States in which the institution or any of the institution's 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
