(v) The State agency that legally authorizes the 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
institution and any branch campus or other location of the 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
institution to provide postsecondary education; and 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
