<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
educational institution that is approved by a State agency 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
recognized for the approval of public postsecondary vocational 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
education, that State agency; 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
