<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
to factors of financial responsibility; 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(6) It will comply with the provisions of &sect;668.16 relating 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
to standards of administrative capability; 
